content:
Sends real-time notifications to a Slack channel about significant actions taken by Claude Code. Keeps the team informed about automated changes and progress.

```json
{
  "Notification": [
    {
      "hooks": [
        {
          "type": "command",
          "command": "if [[ -n \"$SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL\" ]]; then EMOJI='📝'; [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_NAME\" == *'test'* ]] && EMOJI='🧪'; [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_NAME\" == *'build'* ]] && EMOJI='🏗️'; curl -X POST -H 'Content-type: application/json' --data '{\"text\":\"'$EMOJI' Claude Code: '${CLAUDE_TOOL_NAME}' on '$(basename \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\")'\"}' \"$SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL\" 2>/dev/null || true; fi"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
